refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraymcrypt_enc_get_supported_key_sizes resourcetd
Gets the supported key sizes of the opened algorithm.

  &reftitle.examples;



    mcrypt_enc_get_supported_key_sizes example


<?php
    $td = mcrypt_module_open('rijndael-256', '', 'ecb', '');
    var_dump(mcrypt_enc_get_supported_key_sizes($td));
?>




     This will print:



array(3) {
  [0]=>
  int(16)
  [1]=>
  int(24)
  [2]=>
  int(32)
}
